# ChatGPT Amnesia Testing Prompt

```
For this conversation only, please disregard any previous knowledge or context you may have about me from other conversations. 

Treat me as a completely unknown business founder you have never interacted with before. Base your analysis and responses solely on the information I provide in this chat session.

This is important for testing purposes - I need you to generate voice guidelines based only on the worksheet responses and methodology I share, without any influence from prior conversations or assumptions about my business or communication style.

Please confirm that you'll approach this analysis as if meeting me for the first time, using only the data I provide in this specific chat.
```
